<p>Across the country, CPCs significantly outnumber abortion providers, with roughly 2,600 CPCs to just 428 abortion providers, based on data from the <a href="https://prochoice.org/">National Abortion Federation</a>. In trigger law states, their presence poses a heightened risk.</p>

